How to Draw Johnny Depp - The Lone Ranger Hyper realistic Pencil and Charcoal Portrait - Eye, Skin, Ears, Hairs, Mouth, Nose by Sascha Schuerz.
If you like to have also a Pencil Portrait by me than check out my Website please for more Informations.
Website Link: https://saschaschuerz.com

Material Used: 
Board: HAHNEMÜHLE NOSTALGIE SKIZZENBLOCK A4 
Pencils: Staedtler Mars Lumograph 2H - 6B, Mars Lumograph Black 8B - 6B,  a 12B graphite pencil & Pierre Noire 3B / France / 1710.
Erasers: Tombow Mono Zero & Kneaded Eraser
Blending: Soft Bristol Paint brush, Cotton Buds & Blending stump.
